      • getNeighborByWebId

        public Node getNeighborByWebId(int webId)
        Gets a neighbor by webId.
        Parameters:
        webId - The desired neighbor's webId.
        Pre-condition:
        webId >= 0
        Post-condition:
        If a neighbor has the given webId that node is returned; otherwise, NULL_NODE is returned.
